                <p class="location-hero-description">Led by <strong>Reema Jawed, Advocate High Court</strong>, with over 14 years of experience, we're a female-led practice that handles family law only for Gulberg families. We help with <strong>divorce and khula</strong>, <strong>child custody and maintenance</strong>, and <strong>dower and dowry recovery</strong>, always with care and confidentiality. Our office at Tahir Plaza, beside the City Court, is roughly 25 to 30 minutes from Gulberg, so support is never far away.</p>
                
